&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong experience in software/data/ML engineering, including significant hands-on work building and operating AI/ML or LLM-based solutions in production.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience leading AI/ML/LLM engineering teams or acting as a senior technical lead, ideally in a global o

